<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VULNSCAN - Security Scanner</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, monospace;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0c10 0%, #111418 100%);
            color: #f1f5f9;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        .header p { color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 1rem; }
        .cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin: 3rem 0;
        }
        .card {
            background: rgba(19, 23, 29, 0.8);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: transform 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: #00d4ff;
        }
        .card i { font-size: 3rem; color: #00d4ff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .card p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
            color: #0a0c10;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .btn:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
            color: #64748b;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }
        .status {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #10b981;
            margin-right: 8px;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🔒 VULNSCAN</h1>
            <p>Advanced Security Vulnerability Scanner</p>
            <div style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                <span class="status"></span>
                <span style="font-size: 0.8rem;">API Online</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="cards">
            <div class="card">
                <i>🎯</i>
                <h3>Launch Scan</h3>
                <p>Start a new vulnerability scan on any target</p>
                <a href="/new-scan" class="btn">Start Scanning</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <i>📊</i>
                <h3>Dashboard</h3>
                <p>View scan results and security metrics</p>
                <a href="/dashboard" class="btn">View Dashboard</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <i>📜</i>
                <h3>History</h3>
                <p>Access all previous scan reports</p>
                <a href="/history" class="btn">View History</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Powered by n8n + Groq AI | AgentSec v2.0</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.7rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                <a href="http://localhost:8501" style="color: #00d4ff;">Streamlit Interface</a> | 
                <a href="http://localhost:5678" style="color: #00d4ff;">n8n Dashboard</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
